window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I'm a man who knows what he wants and what I want is Birdie.</p> <p>It hurt like hell to watch her leave our small town to set off and chase her college dreams. I let her go once, I'm not letting it happen again.</p> <p>Now she's home for good, and I'll stop at nothing to keep her with me, always. Even if that means tying her to me in every way possible.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
